    {
      "id": "template-contract-composition-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Template & Contract Composition",
      "position": {
        "x": 700,
        "y": -900
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Template & Contract Composition\n\nUpgrade Twilite templates and contract graphs so they use the new composition nodesets coherently.\n\nThe goal is to make structure legible without adding empty ceremony.\n\n## Composition Direction\n\nUpgrade template graphs to use:\n\n- **Template / Structure** for anatomy\n- **Domain nodesets** for subject meaning\n- **Skill / Contract** for automation and validation law\n\nDo not promote markdown into typed nodes unless the structure is doing real semantic work.",
        "definitionKey": "markdown",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
